Class LoadRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jasoncarloscox.familymapserver.api.request.ApiRequest
      • com.jasoncarloscox.familymapserver.api.request.LoadRequest
  • public class LoadRequest
extends ApiRequest
    A request to the /load route. It is a request to clear all data from the database and load in new users, persons, and events.
